  <Docs>
    <summary>Effectively reassigns a workflow task to the task owner's manager.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>A common usage scenario for this task would be if a task owner is out of the office, the task is automatically reassigned to the task owner's manager for completion.</para>
      <para>When a task is escalated, the original task is cancelled and a new task is created and assigned to the user's manager.</para>
      <para />
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
